parser

Class ScrapedData

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.ScrapedData

  • public class ScrapedData
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates an object that holds all of the scraped data consisting of team statistics, including the list of data labels (headers), lists of lists of statistics data, and list of associated team images.
